entries.title_d: This Veteran TIE commander has been a trouble for us for too long. With a skilled pilot like you joining our ranks, we have a chance of getting rid of this nuisance. When you complete this mission, return to Captain Kreezo in Tyrena and Captain Kreezo will train you in a new Rebel Alliance Pilot Skill.
entries.title: Corellia system: Destroy TIE Veteran commander.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Command: < It looks like the TIE Veteran had a malfunction and you will get another shot at him pilot. Don't mess up this time! >
entries.quest_target_d: We will update the location of the commander as often as we can. Intercept him quickly before he escapes.
entries.quest_location_d: A lot of our trouble can be traced to a TIE Veteran - commanding a small team of well-equipped forces in the Corellia region. Find him and bring him down.
entries.failed_escape: Bah, he got away. Return to base for a full report of what happened.
entries.escort_wiped_out: Tactical Computer: < Scans show target vessel escort terminated. No more escort vessels remain. >
entries.escort_remaining: Tactical Computer: < Scans show target vessel escort terminated. %DI escort vessels remain. >
entries.assassinate_success: Very good pilot, we're all impressed! Return to base.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Got him, proceed to the location and terminate him!
entries.arrival_phase_1: Scanning for the Imperial scum now, give us a few seconds.
